      • setExcludesBelow

        public void setExcludesBelow(Set excludes)
        A set of paths identifying the nodes below which there will be no production during the traversal. A path that matches any within this set will be produced in the XML output but will not be descended into.

        This property is useful when Inq child nodes will be processed as attributes of their parent.

        Parameters:
        excludes -
